Player is use mplayer to play mp3 on term.
Also have some options.

How to use
player /home/user/music
#/home/user/music which your mp3 file stand.

=====>2011-6-6<=====
player-0.1
Have r,b,n,l,q options.
q:quit play.
r:play again.
b:back.
n:next.
l:length between current and the next to play.

=====>2011-6-7<=====
player-0.2b1
Improve -l,-n,-r options.
Loop play file under a directory.
Option -n,-r need to be improved.
